headline: Fortinet (NasdaqGS:FTNT) Teams With Liquid Networx To Secure Global Retailer's Data
summary: Fortinet (NasdaqGS:FTNT) has recently partnered with Liquid Networx to enhance data loss prevention solutions for a global retail enterprise. This collaboration likely showcases the company's commitment to strengthening its cybersecurity offerings, potentially influencing its stock performance.
